FIELD.name: OBJID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: unique ID number

FIELD.name: CATNAME
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: supplied catalogue name

FIELD.name: TARGETNAME
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: matching name in target table, used to name FITS files and generate thumbnail images

FIELD.name: TARGETID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: matching ID number in target

FIELD.name: RA
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: RA J2000

FIELD.name: DEC
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: Dec J2000

FIELD.name: PRIORITY
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: survey weight

FIELD.name: MAG_1
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: supplied magnitude

FIELD.name: PROGID
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: programme ID

FIELD.name: MAG_2
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: supplied magnitude

FIELD.name: J_M_K20FE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: J 20mag/sq." isophotal fiducial ell. ap. magnitude

FIELD.name: H_M_K20FE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: H 20mag/sq." isophotal fiducial ell. ap. magnitude

FIELD.name: K_M_K20FE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: K 20mag/sq." isophotal fiducial ell. ap. magnitude

FIELD.name: RADIUS
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: 20mag/sq." isophotal K fiducial ell. ap. semi-major axis

FIELD.name: A_B
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: minor/major axis ratio fit to 3-sig. super-coadd isophote

FIELD.name: MUK20FE
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: average surface brightness within the mu_K = 20mag/sq arcsec elliptical isophote (derived from K_M_K20FE, RADIUS and A_B)

FIELD.name: CORR
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: correction, based on MUK20FE, made to the isophotal magnitude K_M_K20FE to get a pseudo-total magnitude K

FIELD.name: J
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: J magnitude (JEXT) used for J selection

FIELD.name: H
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: H magnitude (HEXT) used for H selection

FIELD.name: KEXT
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: KEXT magnitude

FIELD.name: K
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: K magnitude (corrected) used for K selection

FIELD.name: KEXT_K
FIELD.DESCRIPTION: KEXT minus K (corrected)
